                                                 "scrollSpeed":  -75,
                                                 "scrollTopLimitY":  -196.0,
                                                 "text":  "STARLESS PATH\n\n\nBad Gnome Interactive\nSebastian Einarsson\nSimon F. Nilsson\nHampus Eklund\nDag Ohlin\nGabriel Abrahamsson Wiklund\nMax Augustsson\n\n\n\n\n\nSprint 1\nThe groundworks of the engine\nRenderer\nImGUI overlay\nObject loader\n\n\nSprint 2\nGimp rooms\nRendering bugs\nSkyboxes\nShadow mapping\nScene editing\nUI widgets\nNormal mapping\nVisible raycasts for debugging\nA* pathing for enemies\nDefence logic\n\n\nSprint 3\nHigh resolution text rendering\nCockpit\nModels\nMain menu\nBuild menu\nWin menu\nGame loop\n\n\nSpecial Thanks\nOur playtesters\n\n\n\n\n\nThanks for playing!",
